text: Kabhi mil ke bakchodi karni thi na yrr
author: Nihal  Choudhary

text: Tujhe toh pura padh ke khatam he kar diya bhai itna late mil ke bhi. College ke din yaad karunga toh tu kahin na kahin bakchodi try karta dikhega he. Life time ke liye kuch naam mil gaye h tujhe - Startup, Learning phase, Gocchi ni boschi, Yadush, Ego-driven-Pussy.
author: Nihal  Choudhary
